@startuml
actor Администратор
participant ":AdminUI" as UI
participant ":MatchManager" as Manager
participant ":Match" as Match
participant ":Stadium" as Stadium
participant ":Sector" as Sector
participant ":PriceManager" as PriceMan

Администратор -> UI: create new match
UI -> Manager: createMatch(home, away, date)
Manager -> Match: new Match(data)
Match --> Manager: match created
Manager -> Stadium: getSectors()
Stadium --> Manager: sectors

loop for each sector
    Manager -> PriceMan: setPrice(sector, price)
    PriceMan -> Sector: updatePrice(price)
    Sector --> PriceMan: ok
end

Manager --> UI: match configured
UI --> Администратор: матч готов к продажам
@enduml